<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />帶來的樹苗有著不同的種類，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每種樹苗開花的季節都不相同喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，<delay20 />只要種植不同種類的樹苗，<delay8 />
不就能在一年裡享受不同景色了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />真是太棒了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />的樹苗和花卉種子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都是在島上買不到的稀有物品喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay20 />只要那個人一在廣場開店，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都會偷偷地跑去看，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在可是地球日的活動期間呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在活動期間，<delay20 />我也會送花給朋友們，<delay8 />
或是用花朵來ＤＩＹ喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活動期間還有舉辦特別的哩程活動，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要記得好好確認應用程式才行～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我種的花朵曾經在我的悉心照料下，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在不知不覺中，<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />綻放出沒看過的花朵喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那一定是花朵們
為了向我表達感謝<delay8 />所特別綻放的花朵，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有很豐富的大自然，<delay20 />
空氣也會變得清新，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺一定很舒服～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />散步時除了能在樹下休息，<delay20 />還能聞聞花香<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定會很開心的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
